findings.title: Owner can change safeManager
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to change the safeManager.

findings.title: Owner can withdraw BEP20 tokens and BNBs
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to withdraw BEP20 tokens and BNBs.

findings.title: Owner can enable trading
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to enable trading.

findings.title: Owner Privilege: Modification of maxSellTransactionAmount and _maxWallet
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify maxSellTransactionAmount and _maxWallet, which can lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can change autoDevBurn and buyBackUpperLimit
findings.description: The owner has privileges to modify autoDevBurn and buyBackUpperLimit variables.

findings.title: Owner Privileges: Exclusion from Fee, Dividends, Transaction, and Wallet Amounts
findings.description: The owner has the ability to exclude themselves from fee, dividends, maximum transaction, and wallet amounts, potentially leading to unfair advantages.

findings.title: Owner can change fees and fee receivers addresses
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify fees and fee receivers' addresses.

findings.title: Owner can change swapBack settings
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify swapBack settings, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner Privileges: Enable/Disable Parameters
findings.description: The owner has the ability to enable or disable certain parameters such as dualMarkEnable, autoLiqEnable, limitByDay, and autoSuppEnable.

findings.title: Owner can change _transactionLockTime value
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the _transactionLockTime variable.

findings.title: Owner can change distribution criteria
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the distribution criteria, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can change gas for processing
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the gas used for processing, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can change rewards token address and swapper address
findings.description: The owner has privileges to modify critical parameters such as rewards token address and swapper address without restrictions.

findings.title: Owner can blacklist addresses
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to blacklist addresses.

findings.title: DoS with block gas limit
findings.description: Potential Denial of Service (DoS) attack due to block gas limit, which can cause a function to be aborted with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long addresses list.
